headline: 5 Beverages - Alcohol Stocks Holding Strong Amid Industry Challenges
summary: The Zacks Beverages -Alcohol industry faces challenges from inflation and rising costs in commodities and logistics, while investments in innovation, premiumization and advanced technology platforms bode well. Leading players like BUD, STZ, TAP, SAM, and NAPA look well-positioned.
